{"tid":216758,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大學電話調查員拖欠薪金","createTime":"2017-04-25T11:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T17:46:35.000Z","uid":91404,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bcca723e9b732c0a9ef8fd4ec2ed96ec83cf8d8","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"大學電話訪問調查員一問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/215645?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/215645?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n如題，轉台睇下有冇更多人俾到意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嶺南，公共管治部門<br />\n<br />\n我上個月21-23 翻左三日<br />\n佢話我下個月差唔多時間就可有錢<br />\n但呢家都未有，上星期五我問，佢覆我今個星期一應該有，但繼續拖，我今日問，佢話過多兩星期，因為上個月太多問卷調查，好多人，所以要兩星期後<br />\n窮學生，等錢開飯，果果月岩岩夠錢用<br />\n呢家拖糧打亂晒計劃，唔知點算，無錢開飯<br />\n佢出糧好似當alllowance <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S991Cnr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS991Cnr.jpg&h=e1055568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但招聘時寫薪酬，請問受唔受勞工法保障<br />\n就算最都當allowance ,但將紙講話薪酬<br />\n我只係想早d拎到錢，開飯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做完野按時間出糧唔係應份咩"},{"pid":"62d6b0e64141f5772f19ef85aa350a1db8fcff91","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"求幫忙，人間有愛"},{"pid":"fe7b156f0f0363de6c0d4cf881c4d76b4dfd5fd7","tid":216758,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"大學出糧應該都唔關dept個邊事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打去fmo問下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該30號先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06428d045771c9439e3c708cef155589b523a793","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學出糧應該都唔關dept個邊事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打去fmo問下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該30號先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話要過兩星期先出<br />\n姐係5月10幾<br />\nFmo係咩，嶺南有冇架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係唔到窮到無錢開飯多唔會乞翻份糧翻來"},{"pid":"c842bee10370d52e1b37535bc66a6da2474903f6","tid":216758,"uid":25506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫推"},{"pid":"ac963c2f0aedc95a4930c8afd3f2272bad9efc47","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"點解翻左工都唔可以按時出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以教下小弟點樣可以解決件事<br />\n定無方法，要問人借住錢先"},{"pid":"3f9f2af9df02f4d04e035a5eca61e79b236c8973","tid":216758,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"大學返電話調查不嬲都有拖無欠架啦<br />\n佢地對完數仲要比finance嗰邊搞"},{"pid":"138d877b6c817862468382f1bd69a3a9d9be3359","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學返電話調查不嬲都有拖無欠架啦<br />\n佢地對完數仲要比finance嗰邊搞</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思，佢將紙寫薪酬<br />\n係味受勞工法保障<br />\n遲過30日可以因遲出糧計息之類"},{"pid":"88c3a565f63fa24ed83da03f7f4e09b3d0d8a5b0","tid":216758,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"支付工資<br />\n工資在工資期最後一天完結時即到期支付，僱主必須盡快支付所有工資給僱員，在任何情況<br />\n下不得遲於工資期屆滿後 7 天。僱主如果未能依時支付工資，須就欠薪支付利息給僱員。<br />\n<br />\n違例與罰則<br />\n僱主如故意及無合理辯解而不依時支付工資給僱員，可被檢控，一經定罪，最高可被罰款 35<br />\n萬元及監禁 3 年。<br />\n僱主如故意及無合理辯解而不支付欠薪的利息給僱員，可被檢控，一經定罪，最高可被罰款<br />\n1 萬元。"},{"pid":"0e35cbdc02644eb04e72d31cb41dcd31200f1af9","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大學返電話調查不嬲都有拖無欠架啦<br />\n佢地對完數仲要比finance嗰邊搞</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思，佢將紙寫薪酬<br />\n係味受勞工法保障<br />\n遲過30日可以因遲出糧計息之類</blockquote><br />\n俾我學下，等我得個知字都好"},{"pid":"275a684454eec0cb0922a24980c559552ed9a8b1","tid":216758,"uid":74939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:16:37.000Z","msg":"樓主都算係大學生,<br />\n咁大個人呢D野自己搞掂啦,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學校有你返工record唔會出比你既,<br />\n追唔到個stanley再唔係米直接搵PGP,<br />\n上黎問應該無人會出到糧比你"},{"pid":"2e5935f82c604fd47b078807e786dbdb3e057963","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主都算係大學生,<br />\n咁大個人呢D野自己搞掂啦,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學校有你返工record唔會出比你既,<br />\n追唔到個stanley再唔係米直接搵PGP,<br />\n上黎問應該無人會出到糧比你</blockquote><br />\n我有問佢地，佢地答覆係拖多兩禮拜<br />\n我有睇過勞工法<br />\n佢應該當allowance,不過我睇招聘時寫薪酬<br />\n所以就上來問受唔受勞工法保障<br />\n拎翻應得賠償<br />\n你知啦，香港d政府部門邊得閒理我<br />\n同追數都要有理據<br />\n所以就問下大家"},{"pid":"fdcba8dba6500b94eaa1ccf0a3ccd55452a353c5","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"753f976a113d7f5d9481da348794e535169daded","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"我無意好似之前其他人post,借連登收數<br />\n只係想問一問我受唔受勞工法保障<br />\n求各位大佬幫幫手"},{"pid":"7ab8744537b7818efa380af50cc7411c08ad6468","tid":216758,"uid":91404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"#<img src=